304
00:12:02,598 --> 00:12:04,016
Eli é ateu!

305
00:12:04,099 --> 00:12:05,100
Clare.

306
00:12:06,935 --> 00:12:08,228
Deixa pra lá, Eli.

307
00:12:09,563 --> 00:12:11,315
